                     <interp inst="t18130602-99-off524" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18130602-99-cd525" type="crimeDate">13th of April</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130602-99-off524 t18130602-99-cd525"></join>, in the dwelling-house of 
                     <persName id="t18130602-99-victim924" type="victimName">
                        William 
                        Hall
