                     <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18130602-99-victim926 t18130602-99-viclabel526"></join>; a watch, value 2 l. a seal, value 18 s. a watch-key, value 6 d. and a 5 l. bank-note, the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18130602-99-victim928" type="victimName">
