                  </persName>
            ; it was paid on the 1st of March, 1813; I took the number<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="181306020059"></xptr>at the time I paid it, 646, five-pound. The rest I paid in one-pound notes.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18130602-99-person937">
                  EBENEZER 
                  ARNOTT
               <interp inst="t18130602-99-person937" type="surname" value="ARNOTT"></interp>
