            . I produce a watch. I took it in of the prisoner on the 13th of April.</p>
               <p>Tusti. This is my watch, I am positive of it.</p>
               <p>Amitt. I produce four silver spoons, two table, and two dessert-spoons; cannot swear to the prisoner. They were pawned with me on the 8th of April.</p>
               <p>Mr. Hall. These spoons are mine.</p>
               <p>The prisoner said nothing in her defence; called two witnesses, who gave her a good character.</p>
